<plot>Behind Those Eyes provides a magnifying glass into the behind-the-scenes dynamism of Brad Arnold, Matt Roberts, Todd Harrel and Chris Henderson, both on and off the tour. The movie showcases the evolution of the band, and all angles are revealed, from sold-out performances to private moments off-stage, when the visuals are raw, the music uncut, and the energy so real, you'll understand what truly drives 3 Doors Down, and why it has become one of the most explosive rock and roll bands of our era.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?063610</url></doc>
